    "Gentile's elevation to school director apparently caused rifts between the already anti-fascist Ragghianti.": [],
    "Ragghianti was dismissed from the school in 1931.": [],
    "He then studied at the university in Pisa under <a href=\"/marangonim\">Matteo Marangoni</a>.": [],
    "His dissertation written under Maragoni, was on the Baroque in art.": [
